00:27:10,793 --> 00:27:12,860
¿Somos nosotros?

481
00:27:14,430 --> 00:27:16,165
- ¿Soy yo?
- No.

482
00:27:16,365 --> 00:27:19,068
Soy yo.

483
00:27:19,268 --> 00:27:20,968
